817  }/*for (ihermite = 0; ihermite<2; ihermite++)*/
818  }
819  }// sigma1 != sigma2
820  else{ // sigma1 = sigma2
821  fprintf(stderr, "Error: Transverse_Diagonal component must be absorbed !");
822  }
823  }//isite1 = isite2
824  else { // isite1 != isite2
825  // hopping is not allowed in localized spin system
826  return -1;
827  }
828  }
829 
830  StopTimer(510);
831  StartTimer(520);
832  //InterAll
833  for (i = 0; i< X->Def.NInterAll_OffDiagonal; i += 2) {
834 
835  if (X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[i][0] + 1 > X->Def.Nsite &&
836  X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[i][4] + 1 > X->Def.Nsite) {
837  StartTimer(521);
838  GC_child_general_int_GeneralSpin_MPIdouble(i, X, tmp_v0, tmp_v1);
839  StopTimer(521);
840  }
841  else if (X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[i][4] + 1 > X->Def.Nsite) {
842  StartTimer(522);
843  GC_child_general_int_GeneralSpin_MPIsingle(i, X, tmp_v0, tmp_v1);
844  StopTimer(522);
845  }
846  else if (X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[i][0] + 1 > X->Def.Nsite) {
847  StartTimer(522);
848  GC_child_general_int_GeneralSpin_MPIsingle(i + 1, X, tmp_v0, tmp_v1);
849  StopTimer(522);
850  }
851  else {
852  StartTimer(523);
853  for (ihermite = 0; ihermite < 2; ihermite++) {
854  idx = i + ihermite;
855  isite1 = X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[idx][0] + 1;
856  isite2 = X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[idx][4] + 1;
857  sigma1 = X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[idx][1];
858  sigma2 = X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[idx][3];
859  sigma3 = X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[idx][5];
860  sigma4 = X->Def.InterAll_OffDiagonal[idx][7];
861  tmp_V = X->Def.ParaInterAll_OffDiagonal[idx];
862 
863  dam_pr = 0.0;
864  if (sigma1 == sigma2) {
865  if (sigma3 == sigma4) {
866  fprintf(stderr, "InterAll_OffDiagonal component is illegal.\n");
867  return -1;
868  }
869  else {
870  //sigma3=sigma4 term is considerd as a diagonal term.
871 #pragma omp parallel for default(none) reduction(+:dam_pr) \
872 private(j, tmp_sgn, dmv, off) \
873 firstprivate(i_max, isite1, isite2, sigma1, sigma3, sigma4, X, tmp_V) \
874 shared(tmp_v0, tmp_v1)
875  for (j = 1; j <= i_max; j++) {
876  tmp_sgn = GetOffCompGeneralSpin(j - 1, isite2, sigma4, sigma3, &off, X->Def.SiteToBit, X->Def.Tpow);
877  if (tmp_sgn == TRUE) {
878  tmp_sgn = BitCheckGeneral(off, isite1, sigma1, X->Def.SiteToBit, X->Def.Tpow);
879  if (tmp_sgn == TRUE) {
880  dmv = tmp_v1[j] * tmp_V;
881  if (X->Large.mode == M_MLTPLY) { // for multply
882  tmp_v0[off + 1] += dmv;
883  }
884  dam_pr += conj(tmp_v1[off + 1]) * dmv;
885  }
886  }
887  }
888  }
889  }
890  else if (sigma3 == sigma4) {
891  //sigma1=sigma2 term is considerd as a diagonal term.
892 #pragma omp parallel for default(none) reduction(+:dam_pr) \
893 private(j, tmp_sgn, dmv, off, tmp_off) \
894 firstprivate(i_max, isite1, isite2, sigma1, sigma2, sigma3, sigma4, X, tmp_V) \
895 shared(tmp_v0, tmp_v1)
896  for (j = 1; j <= i_max; j++) {
897  tmp_sgn = BitCheckGeneral(j - 1, isite2, sigma3, X->Def.SiteToBit, X->Def.Tpow);
898  if (tmp_sgn == TRUE) {
899  tmp_sgn = GetOffCompGeneralSpin(j - 1, isite1, sigma2, sigma1, &off, X->Def.SiteToBit, X->Def.Tpow);
900  if (tmp_sgn == TRUE) {
901  dmv = tmp_v1[j] * tmp_V;
902  if (X->Large.mode == M_MLTPLY) { // for multply
903  tmp_v0[off + 1] += dmv;
904  }
905  dam_pr += conj(tmp_v1[off + 1]) * dmv;
906  }
907  }
908  }
909  }
910  else {
911 #pragma omp parallel for default(none) reduction(+:dam_pr) \
912 private(j, tmp_sgn, dmv, off, tmp_off) \
913 firstprivate(i_max, isite1, isite2, sigma1, sigma2, sigma3, sigma4, X, tmp_V) \
914 shared(tmp_v0, tmp_v1)
915  for (j = 1; j <= i_max; j++) {
916  tmp_sgn = GetOffCompGeneralSpin(j - 1, isite2, sigma4, sigma3, &tmp_off, X->Def.SiteToBit, X->Def.Tpow);
917  if (tmp_sgn == TRUE) {
918  tmp_sgn = GetOffCompGeneralSpin(tmp_off, isite1, sigma2, sigma1, &off, X->Def.SiteToBit, X->Def.Tpow);
919  if (tmp_sgn == TRUE) {
920  dmv = tmp_v1[j] * tmp_V;
921  if (X->Large.mode == M_MLTPLY) { // for multply
922  tmp_v0[off + 1] += dmv;
923  }
924  dam_pr += conj(tmp_v1[off + 1]) * dmv;
925  }
926  }
927  }
928  }
929  X->Large.prdct += dam_pr;
930  }
931  StopTimer(523);
932  }
933  }
934  StopTimer(520);
935  } //end:generalspin
936 
937  if(X->Boost.flgBoost == 1){
938 
939  c_malloc1(tmp_v2, i_max+1);
940  c_malloc1(tmp_v3, i_max+1);
941 
942  child_general_int_spin_MPIBoost(X, tmp_v0, tmp_v1, tmp_v2, tmp_v3);
943  dam_pr = 0.0;
944  dam_prm = 0.0;
945  sitenum = X->Def.Nsite;
946  #pragma omp parallel for default(none) reduction(+:dam_pr,dam_prm) private(i,j,countm) shared(tmp_v1,myrank,nproc) firstprivate(i_max,sitenum)
947  for(j=1;j<=i_max;j++){
948  // count mag X->Def.Nsite
949  countm = 0;
950  for(i=0;i<(int)log2(nproc);i++){
951  countm += (myrank>>i)&1;
952  }
953  for(i=0;i<sitenum;i++){
954  countm += ((j-1)>>i)&1;
955  }
956  dam_pr += conj(tmp_v1[j])*tmp_v1[j]; // norm=<v1|v1>
957  dam_prm += countm*conj(tmp_v1[j])*tmp_v1[j]; // mag=<v1|(Mz+1/2)|v1>
958  }
959  //X->Large.prdct += dam_pr;
960  dam_pr = SumMPI_dc(dam_pr);
961  dam_prm = SumMPI_dc(dam_prm);
962 
963  /*fprintf(stdoutMPI, "###Boost### SpinGC Boost mode f norm %lf and mag %lf\n",creal(dam_pr),creal(dam_prm));*/
964 
965  dam_pr = 0.0;
966  #pragma omp parallel for default(none) reduction(+:dam_pr) private(j) shared(tmp_v1,tmp_v0) firstprivate(i_max)
967  for(j=1;j<=i_max;j++){
968  dam_pr += conj(tmp_v1[j])*tmp_v0[j]; // <H>=<v1|H|v1>
969  }
970  X->Large.prdct += dam_pr;
971 
972 
973  /* SpinGCBoost */
974  c_free1(tmp_v2, i_max+1);
975  c_free1(tmp_v3, i_max+1);
976 
977  }/* SpinGCBoost */
978 
979  StopTimer(500);
980  break;
981 
982  default:
983  return -1;
984  }
985 
986  X->Large.prdct = SumMPI_dc(X->Large.prdct);
987  // fprintf(stdoutMPI, "debug: prdct=%lf, %lf\n",creal( X->Large.prdct), cimag( X->Large.prdct ) );
988  //FinalizeMPI();
989  //exit(0);
990 
991  StopTimer(1);
992  return 0;
993 }
